655 //! Write the currency code to a character string
656 #define LOBBYAPI_CreateCurrencyString(strOutstring, uCurrency) \
657  { \
658  (strOutstring)[0] = (char)(((uCurrency) >> 16 ) & 0xFF); \
659  (strOutstring)[1] = (char)(((uCurrency) >> 8) & 0xFF); \
660  (strOutstring)[2] = (char)((uCurrency) & 0xFF); \
661  (strOutstring)[3]='\0'; \
662  }
663 
664 //! toupper replacement
665 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenToUpper(uCharToModify) \
666  ((((unsigned char)(uCharToModify) >= 'a') && ((unsigned char)(uCharToModify) <= 'z')) ? \
667  (((unsigned char)(uCharToModify)) & (~32)) : \
668  (uCharToModify))
669 
670 //! tolower replacement
671 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenToLower(uCharToModify) \
672  ((((unsigned char)(uCharToModify) >= 'A') && ((unsigned char)(uCharToModify) <= 'Z')) ? \
673  (((unsigned char)(uCharToModify)) | (32)) : \
674  (uCharToModify))
675 
676 //! Create a localizer token from shorts representing country and language
677 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreate(uLanguage, uCountry) \
678  (((LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenShortToLower(uLanguage)) << 16) + (LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenShortToUpper(uCountry)))
679 
680 //! Create a localizer token from strings containing country and language
681 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreateFromStrings(strLanguage, strCountry) \
682  (LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreate(LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenGetShortFromString(strLanguage),LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenGetShortFromString(strCountry)))
683 
684 //! Create a localizer token from a single string (language + country - ex: "enUS")
685 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreateFromString(strLocality) \
686  (LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreateFromStrings(&(strLocality)[0], &(strLocality)[2]))
687 
688 //! Get a int16_t integer from a string
689 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenGetShortFromString(strInstring) (( (((unsigned char*)(strInstring) == NULL) || ((unsigned char*)strInstring)[0] == '\0')) ? \
690  ((uint16_t)(0)) : \
691  ((uint16_t)((((unsigned char*)strInstring)[0] << 8) | ((unsigned char*)strInstring)[1])))
692 
693 //! Pull the country (int16_t) from a localizer token (int32_t)
694 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenGetCountry(uToken) ((uint16_t)((uToken) & 0xFFFF))
695 
696 //! Pull the language (int16_t) from a localizer token (int32_t)
697 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenGetLanguage(uToken) ((uint16_t)(((uToken) >> 16) & 0xFFFF))
698 
699 //! Replace the country in a locality value
700 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenSetCountry(uToken, uCountry) (uToken) = (((uToken) & 0xFFFF0000) | (uCountry));
701 
702 //! Replace the language in a locality value
703 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenSetLanguage(uToken, uLanguage) (uToken) = (((uToken) & 0x0000FFFF) | ((uLanguage) << 16));
704 
705 //! Write the country contained in a localizer token to a character string
706 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreateCountryString(strOutstring, uToken) \
707  { \
708  (strOutstring)[0] = (char)(((uToken) >> 8) & 0xFF); \
709  (strOutstring)[1] = (char)((uToken) & 0xFF); \
710  (strOutstring)[2]='\0'; \
711  }
712 
713 
714 //! Write the language contained in a localizer token to a character string
715 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreateLanguageString(strOutstring, uToken) \
716  { \
717  (strOutstring)[0]=(char)(((uToken) >> 24) & 0xFF); \
718  (strOutstring)[1]=(char)(((uToken) >> 16) & 0xFF); \
719  (strOutstring)[2]='\0'; \
720  }
721 
722 //! Write the entire locality string to a character string
723 #define LOBBYAPI_LocalizerTokenCreateLocalityString(strOutstring, uToken) \
724  { \
